::Prowl::

Prowl looks down from his position above the trees at Hot Rod, then back at 
the Alliance bots trailing him. He frowns, tightening the arm he had around 
Iron Raptor. He was getting excited by her proximity, her stomach pressing 
against his, and her pelvic area very close to his own. He flies a bit lower, 
a few shots hitting him.

"Drive ahead and pick up Tavatron," he says through his comm-link to Hot Rod, 
"Then come back here for Iron Raptor. Hopefully Arcangel and the others will 
hold the Alliance off long enough."
